refsection.programlisting:
for i = 1:5
    disp(i);
end

//  instead of

for i = 1:5, disp(i); end

n=5;
for i = 1:n
    for j = 1:n
        a(i,j) = 1/(i+j-1);
    end;
end
for j = 2:n-1
    a(j,j) = j;
end;
a

for v = a, write(%io(2),v), end
for j = 1:n, v = a(:,j), write(%io(2),v), end

revision.revdescription:
The for source can now be a vector of graphic handles.
for is now protected:
Assignments like for=1 are no longer possible.
